<%# locals: (current_workspace:) -%>
<%# Desktop settings-sidebar wrapper — provides the <aside> landmark
    and the boxed sidebar visual chrome (fixed 256px width, surface
    background, right border). For the actual contents (nav items +
    Pundit gating), see _settings_sidebar_items.html.erb, which is also
    rendered directly into the mobile-accordion content_for slot WITHOUT
    this chrome — that's how mobile sees the sidebar contents flow inline
    instead of as a nested sidebar.

    Workspace switching is handled by the header switcher (#workspace-switcher-button)
    added in Phase 2b — the former in-sidebar switcher has been removed. -%>
<aside aria-label="<%= t("settings.sidebar.aria_label") %>"
       class="w-64 shrink-0 px-4 py-6 border-r border-border bg-surface">
  <%= render "shared/settings_sidebar_items",
        current_workspace: current_workspace %>
</aside>
